flavor_text_entries.red:
Very lazy. Just
eats and sleeps.
As its rotund bulk builds, it
becomes steadily
more slothful.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
Very lazy. Just
eats and sleeps.
As its rotund bulk builds, it
becomes steadily
more slothful.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
Will eat anything,
even if the food
happens to be a little moldy. It
never gets an
upset stomach.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
What sounds like
its cry may ac­
tually be its snores or the
rumblings of its
hungry belly.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Its stomach's di­
gestive juices can
dissolve any kind of poison. It can
even eat things
off the ground.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
This POKéMON's
stomach is so
strong, even eating moldy or
rotten food will
not affect it.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
SNORLAX’s typical day consists of
nothing more than eating and sleeping.
It is such a docile POKéMON that there are children who use its expansive belly
as a place to play.
flavor_text_entries.sapphire:

flavor_text_entries.emerald:
SNORLAX’s typical day consists of nothing
more than eating and sleeping. It is such
a docile POKéMON that there are children
who use its big belly as a place to play.
flavor_text_entries.firered:
It is not satisfied unless it eats over 880
pounds of food every day. When it is done
eating, it goes promptly to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.leafgreen:
Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its
rotund bulk builds, it becomes steadily
more slothful.
flavor_text_entries.diamond:
Its stomach can digest any kind
of food, even if it happens to be
moldy or rotten.
flavor_text_entries.pearl:
It stops eating only to sleep.
It doesn’t feel full unless it
eats nearly 900 pounds a day.
flavor_text_entries.platinum:
When its belly is full, it becomes
too lethargic to even lift a finger,
so it is safe to bounce on its belly.
flavor_text_entries.heartgold:

actually be its snores or the
rumblings of its hungry belly.

flavor_text_entries.omega-ruby:
Snorlax’s typical day consists of nothing more than eating and
sleeping. It is such a docile Pokémon that there are children
who use its expansive belly as a place to play.
flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:
Snorlax’s typical day consists of nothing more than eating and
sleeping. It is such a docile Pokémon that there are children
who use its expansive belly as a place to play.
flavor_text_entries.sun:
Its stomach is said to be incomparably strong.
Even Muk’s poison is nothing more than a hint of
spice on Snorlax’s tongue.
flavor_text_entries.moon:
It eats nearly 900 pounds of food every day.
It starts nodding off while eating—and continues
to eat even while it’s asleep.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
It doesn’t do anything other than eat and sleep.
When prompted to make a serious effort,
though, it apparently displays awesome power.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:
It has no interest in anything other than eating.
Even if you climb up on its stomach while it’s
napping, it doesn’t seem to mind at all!
flavor_text_entries.lets-go-pikachu:

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
This glutton appears in villages without warning and devours the
entirety of their rice granaries—such occurrences have long been
counted among the gravest of disasters.
